article.description: Ladan Ricketts had 15 points off the bench to lead Montana State to an 82-46 win over Division II Colorado Christian on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Ricketts leads Montana St. over Colorado Christian 82-46
article.linkText: Ricketts leads Montana St. over Colorado Christian 82-46
article.story: BOZEMAN, Mont. -- Ladan Ricketts had 15 points off the bench to lead Montana State to an 82-46 win over Division II Colorado Christian on Tuesday night. Ricketts made 5 of 7 3-pointers. Jubrile Belo scored 12 points, Harald Frey added 10 with seven assists and Devin Kirby grabbed 10 rebounds for the Bobcats (5-2). Aidan Cantwell had 12 points for the Cougars. Montana State matches up against Green Bay at home on Saturday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
